title: Dadagiri
subTitle: Barkha, a young heiress, is abused by her uncle and his family for her inheritance. Later, she runs away but is captured and taken back to her abusive relatives by her mother's ex-lover, Dharma.

title: Anamika
subTitle: A writer rescues an injured woman who suffers from memory loss but claims to be his wife. In the process of finding out her real identity, he falls in love with her.

title: Howrah Bridge
subTitle: Prem Kumar, a businessman who hails from Rangoon, commutes to Calcutta to find the killer of his brother and retrieve an invaluable family gift.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Tere Mere Beech Mein
subTitle: A carefree country bumpkin's simple life turns chaotic and comical when he unexpectedly inherits a fortune, leading to hilarious misadventures as he navigates wealth and its unexpected challenges.

title: Anjaana
subTitle: Raju, a garage mechanic, falls in love with Rachna but her guardian, Diwan, opposes the marriage and humiliates Raju's mother. Raju decides to exact his revenge against Diwan and teach him a lesson.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Kranti
subTitle: Sanga, a devout employee of Raja Laxman Singh, is falsely accused of killing him. He escapes prison and forms a group of revolutionaries with the sole aim of driving the British out of India.

title: Tum Haseen Main Jawaan
subTitle: Sunil, a navy officer, falls for Anuradha. However, things get complicated when Ranjeet, Anuradha's admirer, claims that she is a single mother.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: 36 Ghante
subTitle: Three jailed convicts break out of prison and hold a family hostage in their home. The terrorised family has to play along, for any attempt to contact the police could place them in the crossfire.

title: Banarasi Thug
subTitle: Shyam must accord with his mother's wishes to marry a girl of her choice. However, when he goes to meet the girl, he is trapped by a man who forces him to marry his daughter.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Dil Diwana
subTitle: Vijay, a playboy, is shocked when his ex-girlfriend, Gita, enters his life just when he is set to get married to his current girlfriend, Nita.

title: Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi
subTitle: When Sadhana marries Deepak, her manipulative mother urges her to harass her mother-in-law. Subsequently, she also meddles in her son's marriage, turning their lives into a web of misery.

title: Mere Humsafar
subTitle: A stowaway and a gypsy meet on their way to a big city. However, things take a turn when they lose sight of each other after arriving at their destination.

title: Bombay to Goa
subTitle: Mala, a young woman, witnesses a murder and boards a Goa-bound bus to escape the killer. On the journey, she meets exciting people from different cultures and a young man who will not leave her side.

title: Satyam Shivam Sundaram
subTitle: Rajeev falls in love with Roopa, a beautiful singer who hides the fact that half her face is disfigured. However, he soon discovers her secret after marriage and begins to ignore her.

title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Himmat
subTitle: Raghu, a reformed criminal, rescues a woman and soon their love blossoms into a happy marriage. However, when the police arrive to catch him in connection with a murder, their lives turn upside down.

title: Hip Hip Hurray
subTitle: Sandeep, an engineer, takes up the temporary job of a sports teacher in a school. However, he gets confronted by the principal and is forced to prove his mettle despite all odds.

title: Besharam
subTitle: Babli is a small-time thief who steals cars in order to support a noble cause. His life takes an interesting turn when he falls in love with Tara and decides to mend his ways.

title: Shor
subTitle: Deepak, a young boy, loses his ability to speak due to a tragic accident. His heartbroken father, Shankar, works hard in order to treat him, but remains unaware of the fate awaiting him.

title: Maang Bharo Sajana
subTitle: Chandra, a college student, loves Gita and wishes to marry her. When Gita's father discovers this, he rejects his proposal claiming that Chandra is not the biological son of his mother Sita.

title: Mere Hamdam Mere Dost
subTitle: A young man falls in love with a rich heiress posing as a poor girl. Appalled by her deception, he severs ties with her. Soon he learns the shocking truth behind his father's death.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Meri Awaaz Suno
subTitle: Officer Kumar pursues a gang targeting women, risking his and his family's lives as he strives to bring the kidnappers to justice in a high-stakes operation.
